            "this to the next curve tenor, that tenor is skipped for that meeting and the "
            "meeting is solved against the next usable tenor."
        ],
        [
            "Fit Error Definition",
            "Maximum absolute difference, in bp, between market TIIE RFR curve rates "
            "and model-rebuilt rates for instruments inside the displayed/model-relevant "
            "horizon only."
        ],
